性别社区的支持</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-trans-people-have-always-existed-and-they-will-forever-exist-just-know-that-pop-music-cares-about-you-3834130">Chappell Roan也做了同样的支持</a>，同时还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-chappell-roans-best-new-artist-acceptance-speech-demands-record-labels-treat-their-artists-as-valuable-employees-3833896">呼吁唱片公司，并要求为艺术家提供“宜居工资”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/clairo-pays-homage-to-lana-del-rey-and-poses-with-gun-after-2025-grammys-3834285">克罗洛邮报向拉娜·德尔·雷伊（Lana del Rey）致敬，并在2025年格莱美奖之后与枪支合影，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
